description:
We are pleased to present 201 Carlisle Avenue, Hebersham brought to you by award winning agent Vedant Agrawal.

Positioned in a highly sought-after location, this renovated family home offers an impressive residence for homeowners and investors!
This beautifully presented 3-bedroom home offers equipped with modern inclusions provides the ultimate lifestyle. Enjoy wonderful local parks and playgrounds, state-of-the-art sporting facilities, charming village hubs, vibrant dining and within the radius of the new airport.

WHAT WE LIKE ABOUT THIS PROPERTY:
- 3 spacious bedrooms with brand new floors
- Open plan living and dining area
- Floor to ceiling tiling in the bathrooms
- New hybrid floors throughout the property
- Separated laundry area with access to the backyard
- Fully renovated kitchen with 4 burner gas cooking, splashbacks and new dishwasher
- Split air conditioning system
- Within walking distance to primed primary and high-schools
- Grass area to the backyard with shed for storage
- Granny flat potential within a prime location

For further information or if you would like to arrange an inspection, please contact Vedant Agrawal 0490 173 525.
